title: [Laphrael's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a varnished golden oak ceiling, an ornate silver samite tapestry hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A silk-covered dress mannequin and a narrow glass-topped table sit in opposite corners while an elegantly dressed maiden statue rests on a polished oak floor.

Beneath a varnished golden oak ceiling, an ornate silver samite tapestry hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A set of carved felwood shelves and a narrow glass-topped table sit in opposite corners while an elegantly dressed maiden statue rests on a polished oak floor.
